org.sbml.jsbml.util

Class XMLResourceBundleControl

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.ResourceBundle.Control
      • org.sbml.jsbml.util.XMLResourceBundleControl

  • public class XMLResourceBundleControl
extends ResourceBundle.Control
    This class provides the necessary functionality to load a ResourceBundle from an XML formatted file (for the specification of the document see Properties). Example usage: 
     ResourceBundle resource = ResourceManager.getBundle("my.package.locales.Labels");
   String myString = resource.getString("MY_KEY");
